This liver study has two diets (`HC_LF` = high carb, low fat; `HF_LC` = high fat, low carb) with three measurement sets collected on 192 mice:
  
```{r echo=FALSE}
datasets <- readRDS("datasets.rds")
dataset <- dplyr::tibble(Name = names(datasets), Description = datasets)
knitr::kable(dataset)
```
